		<p>The <em>Disseminate Learning and Results</em> domain focused on  engaging and sharing information with a range of stakeholders  across the lifecycle of a specific innovation or change effort.  Specific objectives, strategies, timelines and resources should be dedicated for this work as with all others. This domain speaks to efforts to engage stakeholders in understanding and addressing identified needs, selecting innovations, identifying and responding to emergent challenges and celebrating success.            </p>
<p>The Title V network&nbsp;is&nbsp;a powerful laboratory for innovation from which new solutions to existing and emergent challenges can&nbsp;appear.&nbsp;The <strong>disseminate learning &amp; results</strong> domain explains why Title V professionals must contribute&nbsp;to expanding the evidence base&nbsp;by sharing the results of their work and lessons learned.&nbsp;For this to happen, Title V professionals need&nbsp;the capacity to&nbsp;expand documentation of their efforts&nbsp;and share this&nbsp;community generated evidence broadly.&nbsp;</p>
